      • parseDateTimesInSequence

        public static DateTimePair parseDateTimesInSequence(java.lang.String args)
        Parses dates and times from args into a DateTimePair. This method parses the dates and times in sequence, so "5 Nov to 6 Nov 3pm" will be parsed with 3pm in the second time instead of the first.
        Parameters:
        args - the string possibly containing dates and times
        Returns:
        a DateTimePair representing the dates and times found

      • parseDateTimes

        public static DateTimePair parseDateTimes(java.lang.String args)
        Parses dates and times from args into a DateTimePair. This method does not parses the dates and times in sequence, so "5 Nov to 6 Nov 3pm" will be parsed with 3pm in the first time instead of the second.
        Parameters:
        args - the string possibly containing dates and times
        Returns:
        a DateTimePair representing the dates and times found
